posts.title: ATTENTION, ALL PEDES! OPERATION KEYSTONE NEEDS YOUR HELP! The plan to secure a President Trump victory through Pennsylvania!
posts.content:
It is without a doubt that Pennsylvania is THE crucial state to get President Trump across the finish line. All other states are just a cherry on top. With GA NC and PA, he wins with 272 EVs. I pray he will obtain more than that, but this is the minimum.

With that said, Pennsylvania is the closest race by far. Pennsylvania’s nickname is the Keystone State, and will once again be the keystone to a President Trump victory. Henceforth, I am calling upon the patriots of PDW to help me in what I am calling Operation Keystone.

The biggest and best time to push people to vote is NOW! We need an all hands on deck approach to make sure Trump wins.

“But AttackTitan, how on earth do we do that?!”

The independent grassroots movement to contact LOW PROPENSITY VOTERS is how we will win! A low prop voter in Pennsylvania is classified as someone who has voted in anywhere from 0 to 2 of the last 4 even-year elections… so 2022, 2020, 2018, and 2016. Hitting these one-time Republican voters will be crucial to delivering a victory to GEOTUS.

There are TWO mechanisms for getting involved at the independent/grassroots level, both are MOBILE APPS that you can download on your phone. They are:

Early Vote Action

  • iOS
  • Android

and

PA Chase

  • iOS
  • Android

Early Vote Action is run by the glorious Scott Presler, and PA Chase is run by Cliff Maloney and Charlie Kirk. The apps were produced by the same app developer group, but since they are two different organizations/projects, they have access to slightly different voter contact lists based on who their data teams felt were most important to reach out to.

No matter where you live in the country, you can perform what I like to call “armchair activism”. Both apps have the ability to make phone calls and send texts to voters. You can use it to contact VOTERS NEAR ME, though right now Early Vote Action currently has a detailed breakdown of voters by county so you can target specific areas that might need a boost: Bucks, Erie, Luzerne, Allegheny, and Northampton to name a few. I was in contact with the PA Chase team and they said they have pivoted away from specifically low prop voters and now they are just targeting all registered Republicans.

Both apps also have the ability for you to go door knocking. The app will give you a list of all registered low propensity republicans near you, and a convenient survey to fill out when you talk with voters. They present you with voters in a convenient and walkable distance, about 10-20 at a time, so it’s not overwhelming. If you end your walk session, the voters you didn’t contact go back to the generic pool for other Chasers to pick up and contact.

If you live in Pennsylvania, or live in a surrounding state like NJ, NY, Ohio, WV, or Maryland, PLEASE try to spend some time the next two days hitting as many doors as you can. If you don’t live near Pennsylvania, please use one of the apps to call or text voters. It is incumbent on ALL OF US to GET OUT THE VOTE. Everyone, no matter your age or location, can do something to help President Trump. This election is too important to risk losing because we didn’t all do what we could to win.

Godspeed, patriots.
